ally, we release our data and source code to\nensure the reproducibility of our results and to encourage other researchers to\nwork on understanding other emerging kinds of state-sponsored troll accounts on\nTwitter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Nov 2018 19:48:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Feb 2019 01:46:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-12"}
