more, the secrecy diversity order (SDO) of cooperative NOMA\nsystems is obtained. The results demonstrate that our proposed schemes can\nsignificantly enhance the secrecy performance compared to the TMRC scheme and\nthat all the RS schemes with fixed power allocation obtain zero SDO and the\nOSRS scheme with dynamic power allocation obtains the same SDO as TMRC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Nov 2018 01:59:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 1 Sep 2019 12:05:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
