 that our work could serve as the basis and\nprovide valuable guidance to future research and deployment of automated log\nparsing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Nov 2018 15:53:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2019 23:29:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-07"}
